# BAB 3 – METODOLOGI

## 3.1 Desain Penelitian
Mixed-method: survei kuantitatif (≥150 responden) + wawancara kualitatif.

## 3.2 Populasi & Sampel
Banking, finansial, kesehatan, IT di Indonesia (stratified purposive).

## 3.3 Instrumen
Kuesioner (DPPT readiness + compliance), skala Likert 1–5.

## 3.4 Metode Analitik
- Clustering (KMeans) → segmentasi readiness
- Regresi (linear/ridge) → faktor pengaruh readiness
- Validasi: k-fold (k=5), hold-out; Evaluasi: R², RMSE, silhouette

## 3.5 Etika Penelitian
Persetujuan partisipan, anonimisasi, kepatuhan UU PDP.

## 3.6 Keabsahan Data
Validitas isi (expert review), reliabilitas (Cronbach’s alpha).

## 3.7 Batasan & Risiko
Bias sampel, self-reporting, keterbatasan generalisasi.
